Department for Communities and Local Government A monthly-updated list of all financial transactions spending over £250 made by the Department for Communities and Local Government in the Financial Year 2013 as part of the Government's commitment to transparency in expenditure. 

Since August 2013 the department publishes Government Procurement Card (GPC) spend at a £0 threshold.
